Q_NAME: Sum of cube of given numbers
Q_DESC:

The first accepts two integers, second accepts three arguments, fourth accepts four arguments and calculates the sum of cube of given numbers

Hint:

(1^3)+(3^3)+(5^3)+(7^3)= 496
